BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7m-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%C3%A2n-Nguy%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-ni%C3%AAn-t%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-2-Xu%C3%A2n-lai/poem-78W7wlafrNaiQ5YWSIvy6g">Tầm Dương xuân (Nguyên Hoà thập nhị niên tác) kỳ 2: Xuân lai - 潯陽春（元和十二年作）其二－春來</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/Thu%E1%BB%B7-hoa/poem-87ae3Ies42DNGO66rOEEtw">Thuỷ hoa - 水花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/Tr%C3%A0/poem-LD3vA-WExVKONEFMdna0RQ">Trà - 茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/author-LbaVSB66mX6k1U09t5TO2A">Lâm Bô</a>)<br></div>	</div>
